==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Luckiness
<hw>Luck"i*ness</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>The state or
quality of being lucky; <as>as, the <ex>luckiness</ex> of a man or of an
event</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Good fortune; favorable issue or event.</def>
<rj><au>Locke.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Luckless</ent>⟦br⟧
